                 ┌─────────────────────┬──────────────────────────┐
  STATIONARY     │  Hover → Fall       │  Stationary gravity well │
  (Immature)     │  2 m radius         │  6 m pull aura           │
                 │  40 DMG on hit      │  3 m trigger → 4-tick seq│
                 │  Applies StarSicking│  No direct DMG           │
                 ├─────────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  GLIDING        │  12→30 m/s          │  12→30 m/s (keeps flying)│
                 │  2 m radius         │  6 m pull aura           │
                 │  40→100 DMG on hit  │  3 m trigger → 4-tick seq│
                 │  0→6 m/s knockback  │  No direct DMG           │
                 │  Applies StarSicking│  Ticks fire mid-flight   │
                 └─────────────────────┴──────────────────────────┘

Nut's Decree  → moves any star from Stationary row to Gliding row (effect unchanged)
Apep's Maw    → moves any star from Normal column to Blackhole column, or back (movement unchanged)
```

